name: 1950's Retro Chins Up Gal Fine Art Photograph
description:
This is a black and white handcolored photograph from my “Kelly’s Girls” series. I have been working on this series since the 1980’s and it has been so much fun! I get my friends together, dress them up in clothing and sunglasses from my vintage collection and take them out on the town! I have over 100 images in the “Kelly’s Girls” series, all of which are meant to look at the absurdity and hilarity of women’s roles during the 1950’s and even today! 
The image sold here is matted to an 8x10 size for $20.00.
Other sizes are available- from 8x10 to 22x26.
For more information please email me kelly@kellypovo.com
